# Notes DnD and Multi-Select Fixes

## Overview
Continuation of Notes folder management feature - fixing drag-and-drop and adding multi-select capabilities.

## Status: PARTIALLY COMPLETE - NEEDS TESTING

Type check passes, all 221 tests pass, but **manual testing not completed**.

---

## What Was Implemented

### 1. Delete Confirmation Dialog (COMPLETE)
**Issue**: Browser `window.confirm()` used instead of styled `ConfirmDialog`

**Files Modified**:
- `src/components/notes/ThreeColumnLayout.tsx` - Added ConfirmDialog for folder/note deletion
- `src/components/notes/FileTreeLayout.tsx` - Already had ConfirmDialog
- `src/components/notes/TabbedSidebarLayout.tsx` - Already had ConfirmDialog

**Pattern Used**:
```tsx
const [folderToDelete, setFolderToDelete] = useState<{ id: string; name: string } | null>(null);
const [noteToDelete, setNoteToDelete] = useState<{ id: string; title: string } | null>(null);

// Handler sets state instead of calling window.confirm()
const handleFolderDelete = (folderId: string, folderName: string) => {
  setFolderToDelete({ id: folderId, name: folderName });
};

// Confirm callback does the actual delete
const confirmFolderDelete = useCallback(() => {
  if (folderToDelete) {
    deleteFolder(folderToDelete.id);
    setFolderToDelete(null);
  }
}, [folderToDelete, deleteFolder]);

// ConfirmDialog JSX
<ConfirmDialog
  isOpen={!!folderToDelete}
  onClose={() => setFolderToDelete(null)}
  onConfirm={confirmFolderDelete}
  title="Delete Folder"
  message={`Delete folder "${folderToDelete?.name}"...`}
  variant="danger"
/>
```

---

### 2. Ctrl/Shift Multi-Select (COMPLETE)
**Issue**: No keyboard modifier support for selecting multiple notes

**Files Modified**:
- `src/components/notes/NoteListItem.tsx` - Added `onMultiSelectClick` prop
- `src/components/notes/NotesList.tsx` - Added `handleMultiSelectClick` callback

**Behavior**:
- **Ctrl/Cmd+click**: Toggle individual note selection
- **Shift+click**: Range select from last selected note to current
- Auto-enters selection mode on first modifier+click

**Key Code**:
```tsx
// NoteListItem.tsx - onClick handler
onClick={(e) => {
  if (isDisablingClicks) return;
  if ((e.ctrlKey || e.metaKey || e.shiftKey) && onMultiSelectClick) {
    onMultiSelectClick(note.id, e);
    return;
  }
  setActiveNote(note.id);
}}

// NotesList.tsx - handleMultiSelectClick
const handleMultiSelectClick = useCallback(
  (noteId: string, event: React.MouseEvent) => {
    if (!selectionMode) setSelectionMode(true);

    if (event.shiftKey && lastSelectedNoteIdRef.current) {
      // Range selection logic
    } else {
      toggleNoteSelection(noteId);
    }
  },
  [selectionMode, notes, toggleNoteSelection]
);
```

---

### 3. Circular Checkbox Icons in Selection Mode (COMPLETE)
**Issue**: Selection mode showed HTML checkbox, not styled circular icons

**Files Modified**:
- `src/components/notes/NoteListItem.tsx`

**Pattern**:
```tsx
import { Circle, CheckCircle2 } from 'lucide-react';

{isSelectionMode ? (
  <button onClick={() => onToggleSelection?.(note.id)}>
    {isSelected ? (
      <CheckCircle2 className="w-5 h-5 fill-accent-cyan" />
    ) : (
      <Circle className="w-5 h-5" />
    )}
  </button>
) : isDraggable ? (
  <span {...listeners}><FileText /></span>
) : null}
```

---

### 4. Drag Notes onto Notes for Subnotes (NEEDS TESTING)
**Issue**: Cannot create child notes by dragging

**Files Modified**:
- `src/components/notes/NoteListItem.tsx` - Added `useDroppable` hook
- `src/components/notes/NotesList.tsx` - Updated `handleDragEnd` for note-target drops

**Pattern**:
```tsx
// NoteListItem.tsx - droppable
const { setNodeRef: setDropNodeRef, isOver } = useDroppable({
  id: `note-drop-${note.id}`,
  data: { type: 'note-target', noteId: note.id },
  disabled: isSelectionMode || isDragging,
});

// Combined ref
const setNodeRef = useCallback((node) => {
  setDragNodeRef(node);
  setDropNodeRef(node);
}, [setDragNodeRef, setDropNodeRef]);

// NotesList.tsx - handleDragEnd
if (over.data.current?.type === 'note-target') {
  const targetNoteId = over.data.current.noteId;
  if (canSetParentNote(noteId, targetNoteId)) {
    setParentNote(noteId, targetNoteId);
  }
}
```

**Store Methods Used** (already exist in useNotesStore):
- `setParentNote(noteId, parentNoteId)` - Sets parent relationship
- `canSetParentNote(noteId, parentNoteId)` - Validates no cycles

---

### 5. Bulk Operations - Move/Delete (COMPLETE)
**Issue**: Only tag operations available for bulk selection

**Files Modified**:
- `src/components/notes/NotesList.tsx`

**Added**:
- Bulk Delete button with ConfirmDialog
- Bulk Move button with FolderPickerModal

---

### 6. Folder DnD Fixes (NEEDS TESTING)

#### 6a. Root Drop Zone in FolderSidebar
**Issue**: Cannot drag folders out of nested folders to root

**Files Modified**:
- `src/components/notes/FolderSidebar.tsx`

**Added**:
```tsx
const RootDropZone: React.FC<{ isOver: boolean; children: ReactNode }> = ({ isOver, children }) => {
  const { setNodeRef } = useDroppable({ id: 'root-drop-zone' });
  return (
    <div ref={setNodeRef} className={isOver ? 'ring-2 ring-accent-cyan' : ''}>
      {children}
    </div>
  );
};

// Wrapped folder tree with RootDropZone
<RootDropZone isOver={dragOverFolderId === 'root'}>
  <SortableContext items={allFolderIds}>
    {/* folder tree */}
  </SortableContext>
</RootDropZone>
```

#### 6b. Droppable on FolderTreeNode
**Issue**: Folders not proper drop targets

**Files Modified**:
- `src/components/notes/FolderTreeNode.tsx`

**Added**:
```tsx
const { setNodeRef: setDroppableRef, isOver: isDroppableOver } = useDroppable({
  id: node.id,
  data: { type: 'folder', folderId: node.id },
});

// Combined sortable and droppable refs
const setNodeRef = useCallback((element) => {
  setSortableRef(element);
  setDroppableRef(element);
}, [setSortableRef, setDroppableRef]);
```

#### 6c. Collision Detection in NotesList
**Issue**: Note-on-note drops not detected

**Files Modified**:
- `src/components/notes/NotesList.tsx`

**Added**:
```tsx
import { closestCenter } from '@dnd-kit/core';

<DndContext
  sensors={sensors}
  collisionDetection={closestCenter}  // Added
  onDragStart={handleDragStart}
  onDragEnd={handleDragEnd}
>
```

---

## Known Issues / Testing Needed

1. **Drag folders OUT of nested folders** - Root drop zone added but not manually tested
2. **Drag folders INTO other folders** - Droppable added but not manually tested
3. **Reordering within same parent** - May not work (not implemented - only move between parents)
4. **Drag notes onto notes** - Droppable added but not manually tested
5. **Subnotes display** - After creating subnotes, unclear if they render correctly in UI

---

## Files Changed Summary

| File | Changes |
|------|---------|
| `src/components/notes/NoteListItem.tsx` | useDroppable, CheckCircle icons, onMultiSelectClick |
| `src/components/notes/NotesList.tsx` | Multi-select handlers, bulk delete/move, closestCenter |
| `src/components/notes/ThreeColumnLayout.tsx` | ConfirmDialog for delete |
| `src/components/notes/FolderSidebar.tsx` | RootDropZone component, updated handleDragOver |
| `src/components/notes/FolderTreeNode.tsx` | useDroppable combined with useSortable |

---

## Testing Checklist for Next Engineer

- [ ] Ctrl+click to toggle select notes
- [ ] Shift+click to range select notes
- [ ] Circular checkboxes appear in selection mode
- [ ] Bulk delete selected notes (with styled ConfirmDialog)
- [ ] Bulk move selected notes to folder
- [ ] Drag folder into another folder (nest)
- [ ] Drag folder to root area (unnest)
- [ ] Drag note onto note (create subnote)
- [ ] Subnotes display correctly after creation
- [ ] Delete confirmation uses styled dialog (not browser popup)

---

## Related Plan

See: `C:\Users\tjn\.claude\plans\rippling-launching-umbrella.md`

This covers the full Notes folder/note management plan including phases not yet implemented.

---

